description:
Join me, MauLer, Chris Gore, CAMELOT133 and BlueCollarLoser as we talk about a subdued Oscars from a frightened Hollywood, Elon Musk weighing into the ongoing controversy sweeping the gaming industry, and we'll take a look at the first trailer for the remake of The Crow. 

Subscribe to Chris Gore: https://www.youtube.com/@FilmThreat
Subscribe to CAMELOT133: https://www.youtube.com/@CAMELOT331 
Subscribe to BlueCollarLoser: https://www.youtube.com/@bluecollarloser6654
title: Open Bar #87 - Oscars Flop, Games Journalists Destroyed, The Crow Remake
Drinker does Gaming - Final Fantasy VII Rebirth (Part 2)
